              "free_text": [
                " Targets of the enriched lead",
                "isotope 207 were bombarded in the form of thin foils",
                " (7-9 mg/cm2) enclosed in hyper-pure aluminium foils",
                "which served as fission fragment catchers and allowed",
                "re-use of the expensive 207Pb foils."
              ]
            }
          ],
